      "text": "objects and it also had a photo of two F.B.I. agents leading a silver-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "clad man, about one and a half to two feet tall, down an american",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "street. I know this sounds extraordinary, but this is what it had.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "The photo was probably faked but I wanted to be doubly sure. Please",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "write me and tell me if there is any truth to this photo. Also this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "photo was first published by some odd chance in a Cologne, Germany",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
